OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FAs the deadline for applications to
OL,7,Fbecome the UK's first Town of Culture
OL,8,Fapproaches on March 31, towns from
OL,9,Facross our region have made their
OL,10,Fpitch for the accolade.
OL,12,FThe victorious town will be given
OL,13,F#3million to deliver the cultural
OL,14,Felements from its bid, as part of a
OL,15,Fprogramme from the UK Government.
OL,17,FThree finalists will be chosen - a
OL,18,Fsmall, a medium and a large town -
OL,19,Fwith the two runners-up set to receive
OL,20,F#250,000.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
