OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FIn Cumbria and the south of Scotland,
OL,7,Fa number of towns have thrown their
OL,8,Fhat into the ring, including
OL,9,FGalashiels, Kendal, Kirkby Lonsdale,
OL,10,Fand Kirkcudbright.
OL,12,FCarlisle meanwhile applied this year
OL,13,Fto become the UK's City of Culture,
OL,14,Fbut did not join the likes of Milton
OL,15,FKeynes, Sheffield and Blackpool in
OL,16,Fmaking the shortlist.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
