PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FAfter the deadline for towns to
OL,7,Fexpress interest, a shortlist of
OL,8,Fcontenders will be drawn up by a
OL,9,Fjudging panel which is expected to be
OL,10,Fannounced in the spring.
OL,12,FEach shortlisted town will receive
OL,13,F#60,000 to progress their bid, and the
OL,14,Fwinner will be announced early next
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FHere are the towns in our region which
OL,18,Fthink they deserve to be UK Town of
OL,19,FCulture 2028:
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FThe Kendal Town of Culture Partnership
OL,7,Fis leading the town's bid for the
OL,8,F#3million prize, with organisations
OL,9,Ftaking part including Kendal College,
OL,10,Fthe Brewery Arts Centre and Lakeland
OL,11,FArts.
OL,13,FCaz Graham chairs the partnership. She
OL,14,Ftold ITV Border: "We've got a really
OL,15,Finteresting and rich cultural
OL,16,Fbackground in this town.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,F"But culture is a much broader thing,
OL,7,Fit's about who we are, it's about what
OL,8,Fthis town actually is. From the food
OL,9,Fand farming heritage, to the farmer's
OL,10,Fmarkets and Kendal Pride... it's about
OL,11,Fwhat makes the town tick.
OL,13,F"We want to regenerate a sense of
OL,14,Fpride in the town. We want to
OL,15,Frevitalise the spirit of people who
OL,16,Flive in Kendal.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,F"Like lots of other places we've got
OL,7,Fempty shops... we look great from the
OL,8,Foutside, but we have pockets of
OL,9,Fdeprivation, isolated people, and a
OL,10,Flot of young people who feel that
OL,11,Fthere's nothing much for them."
OL,13,FWhile some residents fear overtourism
OL,14,Fand excessive visitor numbers, Jacqui
OL,15,FScott, the Chief Executive of the
OL,16,FKendal Mountain Festival, believes
OL,17,FTown of Culture status will mean
OL,18,Ftourism can be spread out more evenly
OL,19,Fover a wider timeframe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FShe said: "We can spread it over a
OL,7,Fperiod of time. From running a big
OL,8,Fevent - 28,000 people over a weekend -
OL,9,Fwe know the ins and outs of making a
OL,10,Fsafe and accessible event.
OL,12,F"We can use our expertise to ensure
OL,13,Fit's going to be delivered in a way
OL,14,Fthat's respectful to residents but
OL,15,Falso brings life to businesses."
OL,17,FKirkcudbright
OL,19,F3,350 people call this town at the
OL,20,Fmouth of the River Dee home.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
