FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FNamed a royal burgh in 1455, it boasts
OL,7,Fhistoric architecture, and already
OL,8,Fadvertises itself as 'the Artists'
OL,9,FTown'.
OL,11,FKirkcudbright has a varied cultural
OL,12,Foffering, including the annual 'Spring
OL,13,FFling' open studios event, and the
OL,14,FKirkcudbright Arts & Crafts Trail
OL,15,Fwhich takes place every summer.
OL,17,FTwo art galleries and an artists'
OL,18,Fcollective compliment these events all
OL,19,Fyear round.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FOne of the town's most striking
OL,7,Fbuildings is the Category-A listed
OL,8,FKirkcudbright Tolbooth, completed in
OL,9,F1629, which served as both a council
OL,10,Fmeeting place and a prison.
OL,12,FAs late as 1805 the Tolbooth was used
OL,13,Fto imprison people accused of
OL,14,Fwitchcraft, and in 1973 Kirkcudbright
OL,15,Fwas used as film locations for the
OL,16,Fcult classic The Wicker Man.
OL,18,FKirkby Lonsdale
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FThe market town nestled on the cusp of
OL,7,Fthe Yorkshire Dales and Cumbria is
OL,8,Fhoping to become UK Town of Culture
OL,9,F2028, with the Kirkby Lonsdale Town
OL,10,FTeam leading the application.
OL,12,FKirkby Lonsdale's market charter dates
OL,13,Fback 800 years, and the team hopes to
OL,14,Fcontinue this legacy with a victory in
OL,15,Fthe cultural town competition.
OL,17,FTheir application consists of six
OL,18,Fstrands, including a proposed pageant
OL,19,Fcelebrating eight centuries of history
OL,20,Fwith costume and music.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FLocal tour guide Suzanne Sutton said:
OL,7,F"We've got a rich cultural history.
OL,8,FWilliam Wordsworth was one of the
OL,9,Ffirst people to describe Ruskin's
OL,10,FView; we had Turner and Ruskin
OL,11,Fdescribe it as one of the most
OL,12,Fbeautiful views in the world."
OL,14,FThe town's bid is not just about
OL,15,Fhistory and looking back, however.
OL,16,FLike in Kendal, the thoughts and hopes
OL,17,Fof young people are central to the bid.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FMarie Batty from the Kirkby Lonsdale
OL,7,FTown Team said: "Young people often
OL,8,Ffeel unseen and unheard in the area.
OL,9,FWe'd like to get a group of young
OL,10,Fleaders to help us with the bid, and
OL,11,Finclude them in every aspect of it."
OL,13,FMarie thinks the town has much to
OL,14,Foffer the competition judges, despite
OL,15,Fits size.
OL,17,FShe said: "Small is beautiful. Bring
OL,18,Fit on! We'll show them what we've got."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
