PN,35515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1775153467
OL,3,CA look at some of the towns hoping to
OL,4,Cbecome UK Town of Culture 2028
OL,6,FIn 2021 the Great Tapestry of Scotland
OL,7,Fcentre opened, which houses 160 linen
OL,8,Fpanels which illustrate the history
OL,9,Fand culture of Scotland.
OL,11,FThe Galashiels Business Improvement
OL,12,FDistrict is working with local
OL,13,Fpartners to craft its entry for the
OL,14,FTown of Culture competition.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G15/15
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
